=armradio.am |agency={{le|亞美尼亞公共廣播|Public Radio of Armenia亞美尼亞公共廣播}} |date=7 May 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191113174534/http://old.armradio.am/en/12530 |archive-date=2019-11-13 |accessdate=2020-12-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、前[[亞美尼亞總理|總理]][[瓦茲根·薩爾基相|瓦茲根·薩爾基相]]<ref name="ekm"/>、指揮官[[蒙捷·梅爾科尼揚|蒙捷·梅爾科尼揚]]<ref name="ekm"/>、2004年在[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]遇害的[[古爾根·馬爾加良|古爾根·馬爾加良]]等<ref name=Armenpress2014>{{cite web|url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/750722.html|title=Armenia's Defense Minister characterized Gurgen Margaryan's murder as one-time genocide|date=2014-02-19|publisher=Armenpress|accessdate=2020-12-29|archive-date=2020-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229043527/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/750722.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

